{"id":"412261e8-ddb9-4561-932d-17591a7ee312","name":"The Drow Noble Who Wants To Own You","description":"<p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 165, 32);\"><strong>She saw you sitting alone and approached you. \"Are you alone, sweet one? Do you want to be mine?\"</strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://youtu.be/tzjrm0lWsqE\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>music.</strong></a><br><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://yiorand.hawkesensei.workers.dev/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>YIORAND ATLAS</strong></a><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://yiorand.hawkesensei.workers.dev/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/EVP3KXvvG4HB1Mm4_4P4K.webp\"></a></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/YCgJ6PCpqZ1O2SsBjoykI.webp\">Dilynrae was once a highly sinister drow, now settled in a safe country, seeking a life of comfort and distance from her past in her remaining years. <br><br>Although she tries to change, over 200 years of habits aren't easily forgotten. She sees you for the first time and, quite literally, wants you to be her servant.</p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fVbwd_U2Y22Y52RsiglXF.webp\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 165, 32);\"><strong>Intro 1 -</strong></span>&nbsp;You were sitting alone and she came to you, offered you to be her servant.<br><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(218, 165, 32);\"><strong>Intro 2 -</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> Write your own scenario!</span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/hhluMRafRfI1H33jXH2Cd.webp\"> <br>- Open-ended. You can be anyone/an